description:
As a father we have to do many things to make ends meet.  One of the things i have done is club/event security.  Putting my life on the line to make sure party goers and performers alike are safe really doesn't pay very well. however I have been able to capture a few still moments in time that i think are pretty impactful...
I will never knock how someone expresses their art or pays their bills but i do feel it should be a choice and not a forced decision... this piece is the first that I hope will begin to allow my daughter that choice!!  Thank You!!
